      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "Basons.—“Bowls” (mizrāqôth). Probably the same as the mizrāqîm of 2Chronicles 4:8. So kîyôrôth (Kings) and kîyôrîm (Chron.).",
